name: Fremont County Public Health-Lander
notes: Please wear short sleeved shirts and expect to be observed for 15 minutes after your injection. If you have any anaphylactic allergies requiring use of an epi-pen in the past we will be unable to give you a vaccine, you will need to get your vaccine in a clinic or hospital. If you have any questions please call our office at 332-1073, Thank You!
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
